n style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中 国 人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當大家有共識自動標籤   五毛或者藍絲 成為 中国人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地無得反抗 , 如果否認就會為中国人身份增加 負面 效果<br />\n如果承認 , 反對派就識得分辨 邊啲係 <span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span> , 邊啲係反對派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭先實測 , 暫時堆 中国人 未有對策 , 只係一味拉你落水話你都係中国人<br />\n但唔敢否認 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用 <span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span> 取代 <span style=\"color: blue;\">五毛 </span>呢個名 令佢地無辦法話人屈毛<br />\n最多話人屈人做 <span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span> </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反對派嘅同路人 , 今次時事台能否再變得有影響力 , 能否再無咁多無謂亂屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就靠你地喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/364275/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/364275/page/1</a></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6eefb996447504f652b09e99aa90a934e80398bd","tid":363853,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"diu"},{"pid":"a1493eb90808b54c4d491a267a0a26e2b7226493","tid":363853,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcbded25cb282ea53fcafcc0b77ba1fa180784d","tid":363853,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c73f9b57b53ffd7623f7c32f3c1e5d2ba5be713","tid":363853,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"屌"}]}